ationary epoch in the future may provide a\nbetter estimation of the index $\\chi$. Since $\\chi$ is determined by the fluxes\nand vacuum expectation values of complex structure moduli, such observations\nwould characterize the geometry of the internal space as well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jul 2015 18:12:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Oct 2015 22:40:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-19"}
