chemy to systems of truncated\ntetrahedra, rhombic dodecahedra, and isotropically interacting spheres that\nself assemble diamond, FCC, and icosahedral quasicrystal structures,\nrespectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Jul 2015 13:11:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Mar 2016 15:34:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-03"}
